- ENDRJU?

1188
01:19:49,446 --> 01:19:51,946
MARGARET?
- MOLIM TE, ENDRJU!

1189
01:19:52,046 --> 01:19:53,546
MARGARET!

1190
01:19:56,346 --> 01:19:59,745
NE ZNAM DA PLIVAM!
- MARGARET!

1191
01:19:59,845 --> 01:20:02,545
NA BOVU!
- MOLIM?

1192
01:20:02,745 --> 01:20:05,645
NA BOVU!
- DOBRO.

1193
01:20:19,245 --> 01:20:21,344
